  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your emotions and thoughts can tend to cloud your judgement in the heat of battle, so you lock them away by force. You gain 5 damage reduction and once per round when you take damage you can make a Constitution saving throw with a DC equal to the damage taken to gain resistance to that damage type until the end of your next turn.</p><p>Additionally, if you would reduce a creature's hit points to 0 or lower you increase your damage for the duration of this jutsu by +2 up to a maximum of +8.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this jutsu above C-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and increase the amount of damage reduction by 3 and the maxiumum amount of additional damage by +2.</p>",
